page.content: { Gornal}has a good selection of{shops which include{two supermarkets,a {travel agent,two chemists}and{a video {shop.There}are two{Building Societies and{one bank.In}the{village}there are {two dentists,an optician,a {chiropodist,a clinic}and{five doctors {in a group practice. The{village schools}have{one hundred {nursery}and{two hundred}and{ninety {children}in the{First School.The seperate{Middle School}has{two hundred and{ninety two pupils. The{main road}which separates the{two {schools}is very busy.A{recent traffic {count}showed that{1906 cars,114 {buses,413 vans}and{233 lorries}passed through in{one day.
